\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you give me your name and present address please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Mr Henry Bradley, 21 Storrington, Regent Square, London, W.C.1.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Have you been married or are you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I'm a widower.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Can you tell me the year you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think - I think it was 1926.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you tell me your year and place of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, 1903, 28th of the seventh, 28th of July, that'd be wouldn't it, seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 1903. I was born in Cromer Street. That's London, W.C.1. Couple of turnings away from here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many years did you live in the house you were born in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Wait a minute - about eleven years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So that takes us to about 1914?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did you move to from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I moved to the same turning but the bottom, number seven Cromer Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Stop there? Well I should imagine about ten years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember why your family moved house in that street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well was - were several reasons, bad lighting in there you know, there was no lighting like and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 The other one was just a better house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes. And we wanted more rooms you see, which we got.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
I had - well - at that time of day - in between that time I had one brother but - no - one came along very late you see, when we moved to the second address, but I had one brother and one sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were these older or younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 The sister was older but the brother was - one - the eldest brother was two years younger than my - myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How much gap was there between you and your older sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - now wait a minute - I think it was about four years. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Then there would be about an eleven year gap between you and the youngest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's right, yes. Something like that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was that a boy or a girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Boy. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You had two brothers and a sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No I - I don't actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know how old he was when he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think he was about seventy-eight - seventy-six, seventy-eight when he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When did he die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh - must be what - about fourteen years - fifteen years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did he come from, was h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 e a Londo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 ner?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, he was born in London. Yes. Yes. But where I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you tell me what his occupation was, he worked for a firm of sandblasters and then later on in life he was a car}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. He worked for the Stores Coal Company in St Pancras Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was the name of the sandblasting firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 London Sandblast Company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And he'd have been working for the Sandblast company in 1911 would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I don't think he was there as long as that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 He was a van}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 man in 1911 was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I think he was a van - a car}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 man then, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 He was a car}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 man when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did he ever do any other jobs apart from these two do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, that's all I can recollect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did he ever do any part time work or anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Not that I know of, no, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you ever remember your father being out of work when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - no, it was seasonal, you know, your Carmen, coal Carmen then was - all the winter wasn't it, did very little in the summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd have hard times in the summer would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, very hard times. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How old was your mother when you were born, was she about the same age as your father or younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think she'd be a - two or three years younger than me father.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She was - came from London, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she have any jobs before she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes, I think she was at - a cigarette factory when she was quite young you know. And then afterwards like - she used to do quite a bit of nursing you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Is this before she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, after. The only think I know before - about her before she was married was that she used to work there at the - cigarette factory.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of nursing was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She was a midwife, yes, she was - she wasn't State Regis
tered. No, not in those days, no. Help the neighbours out you know. I think she was very good at it because I - I know - I remember her telling me that the doctor wanted her to - be at his beck and call at his private patients, he wanted to send me mother
 to you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So she had a doctor who gave her plenty of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. He wanted her but you see, but she wouldn't take it on, not for the doctor, but she helped everybody out locally like you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Can you give me any idea about how much time a week she spent on this sort of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Oh - quite a long time, sometimes she would be all night on it you know. Matter of fact that's what we put down to her bad health that she got in later years you know. But she used to go to these people who were 
all very poor and quite a lot of them never had no money you know and she - 'course the - consequently they couldn't pay her much. And being out all night and that and - missing meals and all that sort of business, I think that got her down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So she'd often do it for very little money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Oh yes, there was nothing at that time of day hardly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who looked after the children while your mother was out working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well me oldest sister like see. She was a couple of years older than me. She had to help you see, did the majority of it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You lived in two houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many rooms were in the first house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think two. Oh in the whole house you mean? Oh they were all flats, it was a small block of flats like. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many rooms did your family have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you describe the flat to me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - the front room and then the back room like, that's all you had, had no kitchen
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get on for cooking then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I think they had a stove in there but you had - never had no recognised kitchen, you had that in the - one of the rooms. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about toilet or bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No bathroom but one toilet and about - about six - five or six different families had to share that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It was one of the toilets on the landing kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about the next one you moved to when you were eleven, could you describe that flat to us?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well that was just two big room - big rooms, bigger than the other place we came out of but
 - one toilet downstairs and that was shared by - two families you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So the toilet facilities were a bit better and the rooms were a bit bigger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Bigger, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 But it was still two rooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's all, yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house, any lodgers or relatives at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What with us you mean? No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not that I can recollect, I never recollect anybody coming to help us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. My mother used to be at the wash tub sometimes 'til - three and four o'clock in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This was in the room where you had to live too was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, in the first flats we used to - she had to go right downstairs to the basement and there was a big copper there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And this was used by quite a few families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, quite a few families, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Then you couldn't always get your washing done when you wanted it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
No, and there was always something wrong with it what I remember and it took a hell of a job for her to get it alight and all that you know and to keep alight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she have to take a bag of coal down with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh they had to take everything down what they wanted to get the fire going with, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It was certainly a lot of work then wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 Cos}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  dear, what my mother went through in those days - nobody knows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about clothing, were your clothes new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well - if some little bit of luck came along - we might get a new - new suits which cost at that time I think was two and eleven. But - those - those very few and far between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd mainly have second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 hand clothes as a child would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Or what you'd got make it last you for years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where were your clothes bought as a rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well at that time of day there was two places, there was one which was called Summers Town or Charlton Street is the exact name of it but it was called in 
our days Summers Town. And - there was another place was in the bottom of Kings Cross. Judds. I never forget that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was Judds a pawnbrokers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, it was a shop where they sold suits, you know }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  men}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 s and boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When were clothes bought, was there any particular time of the year or just when you were in funds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Just when they - they got enough money - which was very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your mother make any of the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she mend clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She had to do the mending for us, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were shoes new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - if - very rarely had a decent pair of shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was it common to go barefoot in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, oh yes, there was numerous children you'd see running about with bare}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 
-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 feet but - I don't think I can recollect that, being barefooted, but - what - I've had some awful shoes to wear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Awful because they were someone else's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Someone else's yes. Quite a lot of times. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It doesn't do your feet any good does it -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No fear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs around the house like washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I never recollect him doing much that way, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would he get the coal up for the fires or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well actually - we had a coal cupboard in the - in the rooms, one of your rooms you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about any decorating or things like this, did he do that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, he was no good at that. He didn't do any decorating or anything like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So he didn't do much in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would he ever read to the children or give them a bath or anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I never recollected him doing any of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever go out with him without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, in later years when I was grown up I went out with him a few times but I don't recollect going out with him much as a child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This was more when you were a teenager was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You'd go and have a glass of beer or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's right, yes, just it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did he ever tell the children stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh now and again, yes. He related some of his childhood to us you know. Which I found very interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 If your mother went out at all would he look after the children then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well, no, I don't think he did much of that. He had his own interests you know. Go out and see a few friends I think he used to you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have any regular tasks to carry out in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Cleaning all the shoes. Or cleaning the knives and forks. And spoons you know. Regular weekly job, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have to do anything else to help your mother and father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well, yes, being so poor we had to go out sometimes early in the morning and get bread }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
penn'orth of - piece of bread, stale bread it was called them times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be the previous days bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes. You went for three penn'orth of stale bread and they used to give you about a couple of loaves and might smack half a dozen rolls in and all that at that time of day, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Just according how much he'd got left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What the baker - baker'd got left, yes. Usually you got a - quite a daffy for three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pennorth that time of day and then we used to have to sometimes go and get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \endash }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pennorth of pieces from the butcher
s. And - I think at - later years it got up to sixpence }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  six}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pennyworth of giblets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 ta}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
ke the money out with careful shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. Yes. it was us - had to go in the morning and - my brother and I you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was it the children who usually did the shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes. That time, yes. Yes. They had never had enough money to go out and do big shopping like those can today. Sometimes it amounted to eight}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pence you'd go out and get ha'porth of jam in a cup or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be from the local corner shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They used to sell lots of things in ha'porths in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes they did, yes. Happenny worth of jam and ha'pennyworth of mustard pickles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And they used to get a twist of tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes. And you could get ha'penny and ha'orth, that was fish and chips. Ha'penny and ha'orth they used to call it. It was a piece of fish and chips. About four times as big as the way it is today which'd cost you about four bob. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How long did you continue to do these regular household tasks you had, now old were you when you stopped doing them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I suppose I'd have been about thirteen when - finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you continue any of these sort of jobs after you left school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What with my family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you still do any once you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What I did then I started on a milk round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about your brothers and sister, did they have jobs to do, you used to clean the shoes regularly and clean the knives and forks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What would your sister do, would she have some regular things to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, she'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 wash}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 ing up and all that to do you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about your younger brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well he'd probably do the knives and forks and I would do the shoes or vice versa you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you had a set of jobs to do between you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the older children help the younger ones with things they found difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well of course I only had the one elder sister didn't I. And she used to help quite a lot,
 I know she used to have to put us to bed of a night time you know. If me ma had gone out you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Being the oldest girl she'd come in for a lot of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, lot of jobs like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about the younger children, did you help your sister in any way or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, it was not - not much good I could do, I was too young really at that time you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes, we - went to bed pretty early, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember what time it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think it was about eight o'clock, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And your sister would put you to bed when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who did it when your mother was in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 My mother like - well we undressed ourselves and all that y
ou know. There wasn't much to do - mother always seen that we was in bed you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you share the bedroom or the bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, the brother and I used to be in bed together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What were the sleeping arrangements of the whole family, it must have been quite difficult with just the two rooms and four of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, well - I don't ever remember where the sister slept. But I know the brother and I were always - in the one bed together in one room.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No one else shared that room with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So your sister must have shared the same room with your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 With mother and father probably, yes. I don't recollect it though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In the - well bedroom come kitchen. Used to have a bath in front of the fire you know, big tin bath like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was this the room you and your brother slept in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was this the back room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, the back room like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And your mother and father had the living room in front?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Front room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How often did you bath?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh regular once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When did you have clean clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Regular once a week the same, yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did the family eat their meals, which room did you use for meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well mostly in our room - the - back bedroom like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any occasions when you ate in the other one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, if there was a bit of company come we used to have that front room you know and - have a meal there then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of cooking equipment did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well we had the old fashioned - fire, coal fire, with the oven adjoining it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Like one of these ranges?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have gas at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, we had gas after a few years, I remember that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was this a gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Gas stove, yes. 'Cos they wasn't up to date like they are today, then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I don't remember having much breakfast but we'd have a - bit of bread and butter or something like }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  and in later y
ears, when I started the milk round, well we used to finish in time to get ready for school and - my brother and I - and then we would, like as we'd done our round we'd go upstairs and have a cup of tea and - couple of pieces of bread and that was our - b
reakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever have a cooked breakfast at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Don't ever recollect it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It was usually bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Bread and jam or something like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What members of the family were present for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well mostly me father used to go out early in the morning - mostly it was only my brother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where was your sister then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well she would just be starting work round about that time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And she would already be gone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Be gone, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What did your father and sister do for breakfast, what did they have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well me father used to eat pretty well, I think he used to have a - a rasher, but I think mostly he used to have his breakfast out you know. Yes. Coffee shop, yes, which was all the go at that time of d
ay, yes. 'Course he was doing some heavy work then like, which was a very heavy job, coalman is isn't it. And he used to go to the coffee shops I know quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Doing that sort of work you've got to eat well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have anything different for Sunday breakfast or was it the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I think we had a breakfast Sunday morning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 A cooked breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. 'Cos mum used to cook, yes, egg and a bacon usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What about your midday meal, did you used to come home from school at midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
We did, yes, and then another time we used to go to what was called the school meals. We used to go from my school to another school where - this other school was a church school and we used to go down there and have a meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of thing would they give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well - I can't recollect it a lot now but I know that we didn't like it much down there. And it was down - it was like a dungeon underneath this church, you know, very dark. Have an old copper up one end wh
ere - I think they used to put on a good bit of food though you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Stews and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were these free meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, had to - I think the charge was tuppence I think a meal, we used to have to pay the teacher tuppence for the ticket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What would you have on the days you went home? Was that the main meal of the day or did you have that in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well whatever was available, what was going and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 might get - sometimes it'd be a stew you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It would usually be something cooked though would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 If you had a cooked meal midday what would you have in the evening after school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Teatime you mean? Well mostly bread and jam, bread and dr}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 ing I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about your father, what would he have for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well bread a lot - if - got enough money he might - mum used to get a bit of steak or - I know a favourite one what he used to have when I used to go and get it was - gammon rasher, which was very cheap at that time, and an 
egg. And another favourite was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 penn'orth of sketes eyeballs. Yes. Marvellous fish, lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Are these eyeballs sorts of bits of round flesh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Round - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They come off the centre of the flat side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's right, yes. And we used to get enough there to - to have fed the five thousand I reckon for three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2822214\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pence. Just along this road at the bottom here too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would you all have some of that, or just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, father, 'cos - he reckoned we was well provided for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would your Sunday meals be any different from the rest of the week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, it was usually a joint on Sunday you know, anything, could be lamb, beef or pork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You usually managed to afford a joint on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. On Sundays, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would the Sunday evening meal be any better than the rest of the week or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, it might be a bit of lettuce or something like that you know. Yes, winkles, might be winkles, yes, just a little bit of difference.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your mother bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Or make jam, anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about bottling fruit or making pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What about wines or beers or medicine, did she make any of this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your father and mother grow their own fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, we never had no available space you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well didn't know much about them that time of day, there wasn't so many of them about then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What vegetables and fruit did they buy, where did they buy them as a rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well they never used to get - buy much, but we used to buy 'em ourselves when we were out, ha'porth three apples or something like that. Or ha'porth three oranges.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You'd mainly do this from your pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes, well we'd get spares, perhaps an uncle'd come along and give you a penny or something like that you know. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 If you lived in a flat you couldn't keep any livestock at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. We never had any. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many times a week did you eat meat do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I should think about four times a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever have tinned meat at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not that I ever recollect, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever get any extra meat such as rabbit from poachers or anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Buy the - buy the rabbit at the market place, that was another thing that you could buy very cheap at that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This was another favourite meal was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, rabbit and pork. Rabbit and you had the boiled pork put in with
 it, it used to make quite a lovely meal you know at that time of day. Though of course it was very cheap then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you ever remember seeing your mother have less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, numerous times. Yes, numerous times that occurred.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes, we were allowed to talk but - only in - at the right time, we couldn't but in too much, were brought up rather strictly although we was very poor we was brought up very strictly
 and told all about our manners, no elbows on the table and all that sort of business. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd have to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 A certain way, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And sit up at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's correct, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you bring toys or books to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Only after - after meals, when everything was cleared away. Yes, we could then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not during the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not during the meal, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You - you could ask for it but - couldn't say you were going to get it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It may not be there to be had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to have a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well usually it was a bit of what was going you know,
 bit of each like. You might have a - we had a bit - had a bit of everything, whatever was going you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh - used to go off about it usually, never grow up and - you'll never get big and all this you know and what a waste and all that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they make you eat it or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Usually made you eat it but - there were time you could get away with it if you didn't like it really and you stuck out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 But on the wheel they'd push you pretty hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Just - sat where you could like.
