\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever used to share your worries with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I didn't myself, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You were self-contained?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
