\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That was about all they asked of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
