\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, to - not to fight and row with each other you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 To be a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Friendly, yes, all friendly like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes they did tell us that. If you was there and you was attacked by som
ebody you know and - like a bigger boy - always told me to stand up for myself. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
