\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh we usually had the newspapers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember which ones you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think it was the old News of the World, you know. Yes. Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have a daily paper as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, usually, there was the News Chronicle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were your mother or father keen on reading at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No not exceptionally so, no, didn't read a lot.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they ever read aloud to the children or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I don't ever recollect that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember a funeral in the family while you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 A funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you go to any funerals while you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I went to me mother's and father's, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When was that? What year would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh me mother's - oh must have been over twenty years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You don't remember a funeral before 1918?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you taken out visiting neighbours or friends or relatives at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I - yes, now and again we used to visit cousins. Or uncles like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have many relatives living round about or did you go far to visit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not too far away, not, they were - had a good few living round about you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you ever taken out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I used to go with me mother quite a lot shopping. Weekends especially you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who used to go with you when you visited your relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Usually my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you go anywhere else with just your father, did he take you out Saturdays or Sundays or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, all I recollect was a - a ride on his van now and again you know when he was going out a good way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 With his coal van?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes, well - it was a different type of van then to the coal van - we had - you know, when he used to - switch jobs like in the summer, he might be on what they called brickwork you see. Had to load the van with bricks so he had a different sort of
 van what he had for the coal job and I used to go out with him on that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 He didn't actually work for a coal company then, he worked for a general }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 
hauliers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, he did work on the coal company but the coal company used to have this contract with the brick people. Yes. During the summer, yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And you used to get a ride out to the country a bit did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes, bit way out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would he go to the brick fields and collect bricks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. No, I never saw actually - usually - they was usually loaded already on there when }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 he - picked me up at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  home you know and took me out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 And he would take you to the building site where they were being used?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, different places like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, any Bank Holidays or did you ever go for the day to Southend or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Never had anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You didn't have any holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever go away, did your father ever have anything like a weeks holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 N
o, neither mother nor father never had no holidays. Mater of fact the only time my father saw the sea was when I took him when I went on an outing once from the local and I put his name forward to go, it was the first time he'd seen the sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be a long while after the period we're talking about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes, pretty lat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 , yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever go away on a holiday with the school or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Only once I was sent away for a month to Brighton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who organised this and can you remember anything about it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes, it was organised from the school you know and - I think it must have been - I've got an idea, I don't know for sure, but I've got an idea that - might have been the doctor that sent me away. 'Cos a month was a p
retty long time. But I didn't have that month at Brighton I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Can you remember where you stayed there, was it a private house or a camp?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It was a private house. And I - I remember - remember it vividly because outside there was a bit of a gr
een and the gypsies were camped on there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any other children in this house with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, there were others but I don't remember em much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you used to spend your days down on the beach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I think there was a sort of a lady in charge you know, that took us out like and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be a group of about a dozen or so of you would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Could you tell me how you spent your Saturdays in those days, when you were a schoolboy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well naturally had t
o go to - on the milk round I was doing then so I - that kept me up 'til somewhere about one-ish - two. In the afternoons, football mad I was, football and cricket mad you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd find a match of some kind to watch would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well mostly playing Playing. I played for years you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was this local boys teams you played with or a school team?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
School team and - then I got into a team that was older boys than me and I was about fourteen and they was about sixteen or seventeen, and 
I was fortunate that they came and asked me to play for 'em, but they was much older than me. Anyway I played for them for a number of years. Local boys team, yes, though - boys were all at work though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you must have been pretty good to get in with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I was pretty good - touch wood. I was quite good at school, you know, at football and cricket.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What would you do on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well get up and do a few chores, you know, what they wanted you to do, might be run a few errands then
 - go and - and then you have lunch and then we were bundled off to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You always used to go to Sunday school in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any Sunday school outings at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, a days outings like, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did you used to go with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
We used to go to Vrickt Woods, Lousy Loughton as they used to call it then - a place called Loughton. Well it was a regular place for 'em - yes, all these outings went to Loughton. And you had a - big jug of water whe
n you got there and a - pie. I never forget it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they have races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, all things like that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any other social activities organised by the Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, that was all. Oh well, we used to go to see a - magic lant
ern nearly every week, you know, used to have the old magic lanterns then that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were these mainly on religious things or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Religious yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have any different clothes for Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think we did, yes, I'm almost sure we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday or didn't they mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They was more or less glad to get - get you out of the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Only very occasionally. Very rarely really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What denomination were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was the Sunday school you went to Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. The London City Mission. London City Mission or Ragged School Union it was called then those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever go to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. I went to church several times, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 With your mother and father or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, not with mother and father, no. Specially later years because - I - a club I belonged to - while they was building it we had to used 
the church, underneath the church hall. And so what used to happen there we used to have a - afternoon service downstairs in the clubroom which was underneath the church and then a - a few occasions I used to - like - Christmas - over Christmas the wife a
nd I used to take the wife you know, she used to like to go to church and I used to go there. The watch night service. Yes, special service, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How often would your mother and father go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh very rarely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you belong to the choir or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the church or the chapel run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - it was always told - yes, we was always told by the family like to say your prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you used to say them or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not as far as I recollect, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you say grace at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I have heard it said, yes, very rarely but it has been said, yes. Specially so after I came home from that convalescent home. You know, w
hen I went to Brighton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
I should imagine somewhere round about - between eight and ten. And they always had 'em there naturally and I think I was the cause of the upset by when I come home wanted to have prayers said you now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You'd got into the habit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Into the routine, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your father take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Nothing out of the ordinary, no. Just if the election came up like he might get a bit worked up then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know what his views were before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think - I'm almost sure it must have been the Liberal party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She would be more or less the same you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember either of them voting before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I remember the elections on at that time beforehand, I can remember the candidates even. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What year was this, were you still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I was still at school and - it was so much of interest then when they were around you know - like one would be offering t
he people - the poor people in the street half hundredweight of coal and everybody would think they was going to get half hundredweight so they'd go and vote for that man and probably - ninety-nine percent of them would get nothing, it was just that one y
ou know got the half hundredweight of coal, but they all reckoned he'd be a good man because he gave them half a hundredweight of coal you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Can you tell us what you remember about elections in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh and then one - one party used to have the band, I think it was the Li}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 b
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
eral party, had a band used to march round and then when they get to the other candidates election rooms - they'd stand outside and boo. I remember that. They used to come to the - he came to the door and I've seen him
 two or three times - Capital Jessel, yes, Captain Jessel, that was the name, yes. He was the Conservative candidate. And Mr Hugh Dower was the Liberal candidate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You children used to get quite interested in these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They would still make people a bit of a bribe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes. Some used to offer a blanket you know, give a blanket and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When did they do this, when they came round the streets before the vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, before the - election actually came of y
ou know. They'd go round and they might find somebody a little bit poverty stricken so they gave one a blanket you know. They might give another one a half hundredweight of coal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Just to make a bit of a show?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Enlist the sympathy of the people you know and - in the hopes of getting some votes that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your parents take part in any political activities apart from voting, would they go round canvassing or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, they never, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know if your father felt this sort of pressure at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I don't think he did, but we did in later years notice it you know 
but - I don't think it was so much prevalent at that time of day because it was so many years back. I think in later years I think they began - everybody began to notice that didn't they
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When would this be that you're thinking of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I should imagine between the '30's and '40's.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You think there was more pressure then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you ever affected in this way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No I wasn't actually but I - I know that used to be that quite a lot of - places of employment, the gov
ernor was always Conservative you know and - people used to vote that way to hold in with 'em. I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This was true in the years of bad employment after the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When your parents were not at work how did they spend their time, what sort of entertainments did your parents have for themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I think they did used to have - occasionally }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pen'orth up the music hall. It was about three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 pence I think in that day - those days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Both your mother and father would go to this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They'd go together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they ever take the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, we never went with 'em to the theatre or cinema.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your mother have any interests outside the home at all? Did she belong to any mothers unions or clubs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Not that I can recollect, no. I think she was always too busy, you know, what with that - nursing business and looking after us lot.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It wouldn't give her much free time would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself, she used to go to the music hall occasionally with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she go out any - other time to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She quite possibly did because - she had her sister living in the next house to us yo
u know, and I think - well she had two sisters - and she used to go up and see them occasionally and I think they used to go out now and again you know and might go out and have a drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So she would occasionally go out with her relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Without your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What time did your father get home from work in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh all times, it was mostly late though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 He worked pretty long hours did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, long hours. Early in the morning and - pretty late at night you know. Oh no, sometimes we' didn't see him for about a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You'd be in bed by the time he came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 We'd be in bed and - he'd go - be off in the morning before we got up you know, and started again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many evenings a week would he spend at home, indoors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well not very many - he wouldn't be home early enough to stop in you know. He'd come in late and - what they used to do at that time of day - as they knocked off work, being a heavy job they all used to go and have a drin
k you know, all the mates together. So consequently it was late when he - got home of a night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would he have a meal when he got home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh he'd always have a meal when he got home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your mother ever go out for a drink with hour father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Now and again - very rarely though, but she did now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be weekends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your father take part in any sport at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, although I think he was a bit interested in sports you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would he attend a football match or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, he would never go to a football match.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 But he'd follow it in the newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, newspapers and all that sort of business, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did he ever have a bet or go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 He used to have a bet, yes. He used to love a bet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did he ever have a day at the races or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. He'd never been to the races.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember whether your father or mother belonged to any savings clubs, a penny a week boot club or burial clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I don't think - no they didn't. No. No, none of those things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get on with your brothers and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Quite all right, we were very friendly, all of us, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was there any one you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, not particularly close but we was all very friendly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You were all good friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You didn't have a particular one you were close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 NA.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 As a child who did you play with?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well all the neighbours children you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was it a pretty friendly neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Pretty friendly, rough and ready you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Whoever was about you'd go and have a game with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did you play as a rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh in the streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you go to the park, was there a park nearby where you lived or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Regents Park was the nearest but we very rarely got there when we were youngsters. Street mainly, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 There wasn't so much traffic in those days was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Nothing there, and we used to make all our own - entertainment in the street by the games we used to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Can you remember any of the games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I can - tin-can copper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They put a little can down there and - one kicked it away and then the others were at 
the bottom of the turning they had to and - come back and find the can and find you. And then it was hob-bob-bee. Hob-bob-bee, that was a chap stood by the wall bent down like - that and you used to run and jump on his back and he should have to hold you 
a
nd then there used to be about two or three eventually, you know, leaning against the wall and - and they all had to get on the backs. Oh yes. Hob-bob-bee we called it. Yes. And then there was release. And tippy-cat. That was - you had a stick and you hit
 it like that and up come this other little bit of stick and then you used to have to whack it and run.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 If there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I th
ink there would have been, yes, at that time of day, being a bit rough and ready as they were then I think nine times out of ten they would have let him, know all about it you know, they'd had have gone and had a - argument with him, might have even gone 
to fisticuffs.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So these things would pretty soon be thrashed out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
In some districts they used to have what they called rough music, all the neighbours would bang pots and pans under their window and things like this, do you remember anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
No, I never heard of anything like that, no. They used to have parties, quite a lot of them, you know, the late night parties. Saturday nights especially.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Saturday night would be quite a lively night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh a proper lively night. And - probably six or seven fights all going on together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 They were really violent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, they'd fight - argue you know and fight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You'd see a lot of this as a kid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. I saw one terrible affair, it was a street fight, tha
t was with a - frown up men all fighting one turning and fighting another which was a long way away, a long - well, when I say about quarter of an hours walk was a market place and one of these men out of my turning - he'd been - insulted down there by so
m
ebody and when he came back - oh he - well he set about the chap and then from the - market place they came on one particular day and set about all the men in this turning where I lived and it - it ended up as a proper battle with police and on horses and
 everything, trying to disprse the crowds. It really was a battle too and - I think it unnerved me a bit being a youngster because I witnessed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So there was still quite a strong loyalty, the people living in one neighbourhood would stic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111  together against another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Oh yes. Yes, there was a quite a lot of loyalty that way. And one striking point about that was - if somebody was ill - you'd probably find five or six people up to helping her or him - or if it be a male and - one would be one job and
 one be doing another, and that's how they used to go on, all helping each other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 One would do the cooking and another did the washing and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's right, yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So as a child you really felt you belonged to a particular neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Did they have anything like this at school, did you have gangs in the school based on your streets or anything like this or didn't they allow that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, you - you might get a little mob that thought they was better than yo
u you now. And sort - sort of shun you you know, oh you come from so and so, we don't want a lot to do with you, that attitude.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 But this was more the rough and respectable division was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you given any lessons by your parents or anyone before you started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 When you first started did you go for the whole day or just in the mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 As far as I recollect it was the whole day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you remember what the hours were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I think it was nine 'til three. As far as I can recollect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What kind of school was this, was it a church school or a board school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, L.C.C.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was it a mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Mixed, yes. Well as regards th
e infants, which I would be at that time, but after that, no, it wasn't mixed. They had a boys department and a girls department after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was this in the same school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In the same school. Different floors - as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How many schools did you go to, when did you leave this first school,?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I never left there, I stopped there all the time, right 'til I was fourteen. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh walked, it wasn't far, it was only down the side turning from where I lived you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - in the early days I - I seem - think it must have been me mother took me. But after that, brother and I used to walk down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did you have your midday meal while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well some
times we used to have - would come home. Other times we would have a school meal which would be - sent from my school to a church school about - five or ten minutes walk away, used to go there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you'd go along to the church school for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, for the meal, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was school meals a regular thing in those days, what sort of thing did you have for the school meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I know it wasn't too good and I was never struck on it. And especially as it was in such a dreary place, it was u
nderneath the church and it was very dull down there and the food I didn't like at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 About how often would you go there for a midday meal, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Two or three times a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What did you think of school on the whole, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I rather liked it but - all according to what - teacher you were under.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - some I liked very much and others I thought were - well a bit beyond it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In what way do you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well we had one particular - schoolteacher, he used to keep a black ruler - round ruler - on his desk and if you were sitting at your desk and you moved in any sort of w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 
ay he would think nothing of sh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13769809\charrsid8211111 ow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 ing this and it was pretty heavy too and it coul
d hurt you quite a lot you know, and one day he did this too often, it - it bounced off the desk and went out of the window, and somebody picked it up in the - in the playground and somehow or other he couldn't find it anymore.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This would be just for moving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Discipline was pretty strict then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12923626\charrsid8211111 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
rribly strict then, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were all the teachers strict?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Not - no, not all of them. No, one or two I liked very much you know, very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life, like tidiness or cleanliness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Oh yes, they was important. They was all for that. But - oh regular attendance they - used to harp on a lot. And I was so good at that that I used to have a row of medals across me chest like Goring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You used to get one of these a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes. And - they start off with being bronze and then they go up to a silver colour and then they would go back - to like a gold colour with bars on. And I think I had somewhere in the region of about seven of these.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was there much absenteeism in those days, you obviously attended regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh regular every day, yes. No, I couldn't say there was - there was very little - you might find a boy out about one morning in the
 week - usually - probably see him back again in the afternoon. No, there wasn't much absenteeism.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You say this one teacher used to throw this ruler at you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was the general punishment if you did something the teachers disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well the cane. We always got the cane, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any other sorts of punishments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well not laid down but - one particular teacher, his punishment was very funny. He would pull one cheek out like that and hit hou on the other cheek. Yes, his particular method.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Was there much of this sort of casual belt round the ears rather than the cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, mostly - if you'd been a bit naughty the teacher would say, right you've got to see the headmaster. And he'd go in front of the he
admaster and he would give you the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were the other teachers allowed to cane you or just the head?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, the teachers were allowed to cane you as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you know whether the girls got the cane as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I couldn't - couldn't say about the girls.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Yes. And - I think me mother was a bit of a firebrand, if she thought that I'd got a whacking there at school she would - go up there after 'em, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did she meet the teachers apart from this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, I don't think there was any of that at that time of day, no there wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Parents would just go up if they felt something was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Wrong, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. The majority of them did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, I think so, yes. I - it seemed to be sort of - bit of favouritism as far as was concerned at th
at time of day you know. If they was a bit - smartly dressed you know in comparison to us poor ones then they seemed to get preferential treatment you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were there any children left out of things?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, quite a good bit I think. And it seemed to be that the poorer ones, you know, were the ones that were left out of things mostly.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You think if you were raggedly dressed you'd be left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 That's right, yes. You might not be invited to take part in the play and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So it's more activities out of the classroom where you'd get forgotten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I - at the time no, I don't think I would have done because I knew the family weren't too well off and weren't doing too we-l you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In one way yes,
 that - in another no. I think I've gone pretty - done pretty well without it, although at the same time I think I could have gone farther had I - took on a bit more education.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15086643\charrsid8211111  you think you bene}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 fited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 While you were at school did you have any part time job or any means of earning regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I was a - a boy on a milk round, I used to help the milkman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 This was regular every morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Every morning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How old were you when you started doing this?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I was about - between eleven and twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were you doing this until you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well just the milk - I know a boy that worked on there and he - he was leaving and he r
ecommended me to the milkman, then the milkman came and asked me if I would do the job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What exactly did you have to do in this job, what hours did you work and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well we went about - seven - between six and seven in the mornin
g 'til up to school time. So you can say near enough about quarter to nine, and we used to run upstairs and I - wash and get ready for school. And then on Sunday - Saturdays and Sundays it would be about three times you'd go out - three different rounds t
hey used to do at that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So it was quite a lot of hours you worked really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Quite a lot of hours really and it was quite hard work, I mean in the winter, carrying them cans - all them milk cans up and down the flats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of cans did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Milk cans with a handle on you know, they all had a handle. They ranged from half a pint up to about a quart. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would you have the milk in big churns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 On the - on the barrow yes, that you're - your milkman pushed and y
ou was there helping him to push it you know, with the milk church in the middle of the barrow, that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How much did you get paid for this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 At that time I think it was two shillings - I used to get paid - by the milkman himself a
nd sixpence from the governor that owne the shop - dairy. So it made up to half a crown a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you think that was a fair wage at the time or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 At the time I did, yes, because - a farthing even was something to posses then at that time of day. Yes, I was doing all right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you give any of this money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, I used to give her the two shillings you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was this spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well help her out with - at home, yes, food and different things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you get any of this money back as pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Might get a farthing here and there and - or - if we got a ha'penny we were rich.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you were really doing this ......?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 More to help out at home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You didn't get very much out of it yourself at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
No. But I will say that now and again we used to get a - copper or so from the customers themselves. That would be mine, just now and again they used to take pity on you you know or - be thankful to you for bringing their milk in e
arly an the morning and that. And one or two of 'em would show their appreciation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Nowadays people usually give tradesmen something at Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you do quite well at Christmastime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, pretty well you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh pretty good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well him and his wife were funny pair. They used to get annoyed over different things you know, flare up. And I remember her coming down one day and 
giving a couple of boys a whack and we used to have to go down into a - a area sort of place, and wash the cans up in a big tub and something - annoyed her and she came down, I remember her whacking two of the boys round the face.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you feel about your employers on the average?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well - the employer that I had there? Well I thought he was rather on the tight side. Because we worked so many rounds on the Christmas Day and - on the Sunday he used to come out and he usually used to be a penny u
sed to give you extra on the Sunday you see. Well this being at Christmastime he'd called us all together and he said to me, here you are Harry, there's a little extra between you and the boys - for you and the boys. I held out me hand and I thought it wa
s a half sovereign than he'd given me and so did the other boys, until I pointed out to 'em that it was a farthing - a new farthing and - they was all terribly disappointed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You were more or less head boy by then were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I'd been there the longest you see and he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you like the work on the whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well not particularly, no. You was out in the winter as well you know and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You just did it out of duty for your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Family more or less, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No I don't think it did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever have any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, that was the only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I was working for a branch of the Imperial Tobacco Company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of work was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well I used to do what they called - as a boy when I first started - what they call devilling. That was the tobacco ran through a band and through cogs and they just tore the tobacco up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I - a neighbour - which - who - female - worked there and she recommended me there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What hours did you work in this job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Half past seven - 'til - quarter to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Saturdays was - twelve o'clock. Half past seven 'til twelve you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have any holidays with pay on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes, they - you got paid holiday after you'd been there a twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What were you paid on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What my wages? Oh well, when I first started there it was eleven shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you think that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, at that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you give any of this money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh it all went to me mother bar about - a shilling or two bob out of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 She'd give you this back would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you get on with the people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Oh pretty good. 'Course as a young boy then in - in the factories and that you would always be - lacky and the underdog you know, as a young boy like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did you feel about the work, did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No I didn't, not to start with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How did your employer treat you at that stage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh well - pretty fair, but you didn't see him much. Not the governor. Mostly you had the fo
reman and the under-foreman over you. So they saw more of you all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did starting full time work change your attitude to school in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No. Couldn't say it did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What jobs have you done since 1918, what sort of work have you done since then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I had forty-two years of that one particular firm. Then I came out and I worked for the Ministry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What Ministry was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I worked for the Treasury and then I went from the Treasury to another Ministry, which is called Ne
ddy. National Economic Development Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What were you doing at the Ministries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
I was a messenger at the Treasury at first and then after a number of years I got promoted to senior messenger. So I had two or three under me then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You started off in the tobacco works minding this machine, did you do this sort of work all the time you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh - no, I got - put on numerous jobs, and eventually I finished up, well - well I was promoted there, I was what they call a charge}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15086643\charrsid8211111 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 hand, which put me in charge of the stockroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would you have pre}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15086643\charrsid8211111 f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 erred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well I did prefer it in the first onset which was electrician, to go into the electricity business. I would have liked that but - when I went to the Labou
r Exchange they sent me after several of these jobs which I told 'em I wanted an electricity job and when I got to two or three of them I - I find that they was none of them electricians, one was a press tool maker, all different kinds of places they sent
 me to, what for I don't know - I've never found out about that since. But that's what they did with me, when I asked for electricians that's where they sent me. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period for any of these jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you belong to a trade union or anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 I did, yes, at the - tobacco - well I even did for a while while I was at the - with the Ministry,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you ever take part in any of the union activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, I - I - actually I finished up as a - a steward of the union in the tobacco factory.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you feel that the employers and workers had the same interests or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What way do you mean same interests? Interest in the firm or -? Oh no, they clashed quite a lot you
 know. And - rather peculiar - they brought in - anybody into the - on the managerial side and he hadn't been there no time and he knew it all, probably you'd been there years and he knew it all he reckoned }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15086643\charrsid8211111 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 bove you you know
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you think there was a conflict between management and men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Even in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 In how the job should run and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Do you feel that there was any division between craftsmen and other workers, did you feel it in those job or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well I noticed it because there was such a difference in the money, you know, the rate of pay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Up 'til 1918? Oh yes, all the time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 No, although I was able to help a bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You felt slightly more independent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How about with your brothers and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well they were the same, they - 'cos they were working full time then and - they all used to chip in a bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you spend your Sunday any differently after you left school, did you still go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Still went to Sunday school, yes, for a good while.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you take any interest in politics at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - I didn't take any interest in 'em but I was getting more interested in 'em because - seemed to be hearing more of
 'em then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 It was quite an interest after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What were your political views then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - I - my views were that - if a man was doing a good job he should get paid for it. Paid a - a proper wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How would you have voted if you had have been old enough to vote at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well - I would have voted for the candidate that could have - gave that as his views too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You didn't support any particular party then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well yes, I felt I did - there - 
there was only two parties then. There was the Liberals and the Conservatives. And I felt then at that particular time as I supported the Liberals point of view more than any - the Conservatives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you make any new friends at this time, when you first started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes. Yes I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Where did you meet them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well I - I joined the club see and I met quite a lot of - new friends at the club. Even some of those that wouldn't tolerate me when I was at school with 'em but when I got to the club there, after a while I got quite friendly with those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 What sort of club was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well it was a boys club. And - too, part in all kinds of sports, football, cricket, boxing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You think you got accepted through that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Through that, yes, abilities at that yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you bring your friends home at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 How and again, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you go out in the evening, anywhere else other than the club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes, now and again we'd go to a cinema, or - music hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 
Well - quite often - oh one chap I - he lived in my own turning but he belonged to the club with me as well and we became thick friends and I used to be out with him practically every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did you have any other special friends at this time? Or just this one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Well about three or four all out of the same turning and they'd all join the club round about the same time as me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Were these just boys or boys and -irls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Just boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they expect you to be in by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Did they expect to know where you were going when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 So you still had to keep your parents informed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16720563 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 More or less yes you did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3287634 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14160326\charrsid8211111 You say you thought joining this club was one of the finest things that happened to you?
